Fast-rising act, Fireboy DML  previously released single “Jealous”, which gained massive acceptance and increased his fanbase. With many questioning whether or not he could keep up with releasing good songs, he answered their questions with yet another single ‘What If I Say’. The video which was shot on what seems to be an island features Fireboy professing his undying love to his ‘boo’ and his plans for them to elope. From the lyrics, beat and quality of the video, we know not to expect any less in the coming months. At least, we all know he’s no longer Jealous and has a seemingly steady love life now. Watch the video below: 